This paper involves the use of deep neural networks for image analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for predicting diabetes, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of medical images, which could potentially fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
